msgid ""
"Chaḍḍetha, bho, purāṇāni tiṇāni kaṭṭhāni udakāni, lahubhārehi sakaṭehi "
"sīghaṃ sīghaṃ gacchatha, mā yoggāni kilamitthā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Toss out your grass, wood, and water. Your wagons will move swiftly when "
"lightly-laden, so don’t tire your draught teams.’"

