msgid ""
"Chaḍḍetha, bho, purāṇāni tiṇāni kaṭṭhāni udakāni, lahubhārehi sakaṭehi "
"sīghaṃ sīghaṃ gacchatha;"
msgstr ""
"He advises us to toss out the grass, wood, and water. The wagons will move "
"swiftly when lightly-laden, and won’t tire our draught teams."

#, fuzzy
msgctxt "dn23:50.5"
msgid "mā yoggāni kilamitthā”ti."
msgstr "  "

msgctxt "dn23:50.6"
msgid ""
"Ayaṃ bho puriso neva amhākaṃ mitto, na ñātisālohito, kathaṃ mayaṃ imassa "
"saddhāya gamissāma."
msgstr ""
"But this person is nor our friend or relative. How can we proceed out of "
"trust in him?"

msgctxt "dn23:50.7"
msgid ""
"Na vo chaḍḍetabbāni purāṇāni tiṇāni kaṭṭhāni udakāni, yathābhatena bhaṇḍena "
"satthaṃ payāpetha."
msgstr ""
"We shouldn’t toss out any grass, wood, and water, but continue with our "
"goods laden as before."

msgctxt "dn23:50.8"
msgid "Na no purāṇaṃ chaḍḍessāmā’ti."
msgstr "We shall not toss out any old stock.’"

msgctxt "dn23:50.9"
msgid ""
"‘Evaṃ, bho’ti kho te satthikā tassa satthavāhassa paṭissutvā yathābhatena "
"bhaṇḍena satthaṃ payāpesuṃ."
msgstr ""
"‘Yes, sir,’ the drivers replied, and they restarted the caravan with the "
"goods laden as before."

msgctxt "dn23:50.10"
msgid "Te paṭhamepi satthavāse na addasaṃsu tiṇaṃ vā kaṭṭhaṃ vā udakaṃ vā."
msgstr "And in the caravan’s first campsite they saw no grass, wood, or water."

msgctxt "dn23:50.11"
msgid "Dutiyepi satthavāse …"
msgstr "And in the second,"

msgctxt "dn23:50.12"
msgid "tatiyepi satthavāse …"
msgstr "third,"

msgctxt "dn23:50.13"
msgid "catutthepi satthavāse …"
msgstr "fourth,"

msgctxt "dn23:50.14"
msgid "pañcamepi satthavāse …"
msgstr "fifth,"

msgctxt "dn23:50.15"
msgid "chaṭṭhepi satthavāse …"
msgstr "sixth,"

msgctxt "dn23:50.16"
msgid "sattamepi satthavāse na addasaṃsu tiṇaṃ vā kaṭṭhaṃ vā udakaṃ vā."
msgstr "and seventh campsites they saw no grass, wood, or water."

msgctxt "dn23:50.17"
msgid "Tañca satthaṃ addasaṃsu anayabyasanaṃ āpannaṃ."
msgstr "And they saw the other caravan that had come to ruin."

msgctxt "dn23:50.18"
msgid ""
"Ye ca tasmiṃ satthepi ahesuṃ manussā vā pasū vā, tesañca aṭṭhikāneva "
"addasaṃsu tena yakkhena amanussena bhakkhitānaṃ."
msgstr ""
"And they saw the bones of the men and beasts who had been devoured by that "
"non-human spirit."

#. </p><p><a class="sc" id="36"></a>
msgctxt "dn23:51.1"
msgid "Atha kho so satthavāho satthike āmantesi:"
msgstr "So the caravan leader addressed his drivers:"

msgctxt "dn23:51.2"
msgid ""
"‘ayaṃ kho, bho, sattho anayabyasanaṃ āpanno, yathā taṃ tena bālena "
"satthavāhena pariṇāyakena."
msgstr ""
"‘This caravan came to ruin, as happens when guided by a foolish caravan "
"leader."

msgctxt "dn23:51.3"
msgid ""
"Tena hi, bho, yānamhākaṃ satthe appasārāni paṇiyāni, tāni chaḍḍetvā, yāni "
"imasmiṃ satthe mahāsārāni paṇiyāni, tāni ādiyathā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Well then, sirs, toss out any of our merchandise that’s of little value, and "
"take what’s valuable from this caravan.’"

msgctxt "dn23:51.4"
msgid ""
"‘Evaṃ, bho’ti kho te satthikā tassa satthavāhassa paṭissutvā yāni sakasmiṃ "
"satthe appasārāni paṇiyāni, tāni chaḍḍetvā yāni tasmiṃ satthe mahāsārāni "
"paṇiyāni, tāni ādiyitvā sotthinā taṃ kantāraṃ nitthariṃsu, yathā taṃ "
"paṇḍitena satthavāhena pariṇāyakena."
msgstr ""
"‘Yes, sir’ rplied the drivers, and that’s what they did. They crossed over "
"the desert safely, as happens when guided by an astute caravan leader."

msgctxt "dn23:51.5"
msgid ""
"Evameva kho tvaṃ, rājañña, bālo abyatto anayabyasanaṃ āpajjissasi ayoniso "
"paralokaṃ gavesanto, seyyathāpi so purimo satthavāho."
msgstr ""
"In the same way, chieftain, being foolish and incompetent, you will come to "
"ruin seeking the other world irrationally, like the first caravan leader."

#. VAR: saddhātabbaṃ → saddahātabbaṃ (bj, pts1, mr)
#. VAR: tava → te (mr)
msgctxt "dn23:51.6"
msgid ""
"Yepi tava sotabbaṃ saddhātabbaṃ maññissanti, tepi anayabyasanaṃ "
"āpajjissanti, seyyathāpi te satthikā."
msgstr ""
"And those who think you’re listening to and trusting will also come to ruin, "
"like the drivers."

msgctxt "dn23:51.7"
msgid "Paṭinissajjetaṃ, rājañña, pāpakaṃ diṭṭhigataṃ;"
msgstr ""
"Let go of this harmful misconception, chieftain, let go of it! Don’t create "
"lasting harm and suffering for yourself!”"

