msgstr ""
"‘This pile of abandoned sunn hemp cloth is just what we wanted the hemp and "
"hemp thread for!"

msgctxt "dn23:63.4"
msgid ""
"Tena hi, samma, tvañca sāṇabhāraṃ chaḍḍehi, ahañca sāṇasuttabhāraṃ "
"chaḍḍessāmi, ubho sāṇibhāraṃ ādāya gamissāmā’ti."
msgstr ""
"Well then, my friend, let’s abandon our bundles, and both take a bundle of "
"hemp cloth and go on.’"

msgctxt "dn23:63.5"
msgid ""
"‘Ayaṃ kho me, samma, sāṇabhāro dūrābhato ca susannaddho ca, alaṃ me, tvaṃ "
"pajānāhī’ti."
msgstr ""
"‘I’ve already carried this bundle of hemp a long way, and it’s well tied up. "
